<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[الإِشطاء]</span>: أشطأت الشجرةُ،<span class="c5"> مهموز:</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
